Map of most cultivated crops testr

This map shows the most cultivated crop for each country (by harvested area). The most common crops are mainly cereals (wheat, maize, rice, barley and millet), with also a strong share of soybeans in the Americas. Beyond these main crops, some countries are specialized in other crops (such as coffee or oil palm).

Data: FAO | Map: Benjamin Nowak
